---
import { business } from '../data/site';
---
<section id="contacte" class="cta">
  <div class="wrap cta-box reveal">
    <div>
      <span class="kicker light">Contacte</span>
      <h2>Tens una peça per arreglar o una idea per crear?</h2>
      <p>
        Demana cita al taller i explica què necessites. Pots consultar primer per WhatsApp o escriure per Instagram.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-actions">
      <a class="btn" href={business.instagram} target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>
      <a class="btn alt" href={business.whatsapp}>WhatsApp</a>
      <a class="btn alt" href={business.maps}>Google Maps</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
